BlaineDialogue: ^COSMO: Woah you look so buff and muscular! Are you a bodybuilder?!
^BLAINE: Well that’s quite the compliment! But no, these muscles were formed from all the labour us Calmaaj do out in the fields!
TheRest: ^BLAINE: Why yes, our tribe revolves heavily around agriculture. We sow seeds and cultivate them in collaboration from the Pluvia to provide produce for all to enjoy!
^COSMO: Wow! So you can get THIS toned and muscular just by planting vegetables all day? Cielle you better get on it! You’re looking a little twiggy...
^BLAINE: Hahaha! It is hard work at times… but the results are worth it! Why, the majority of the produce you see in this market are the fruits (and vegetables) of our labour!
^BLAINE: Be sure to look around at all the stalls in the market to see the variety of stuff we all have! Now you two have a great day, ok?
